00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:16,940
so that his name was much set by.

221
00:09:16,940 --> 00:09:18,539
That phrase at the end of verse number 30

222
00:09:18,539 --> 00:09:22,479
means that it was held in high regard and high esteem.

223
00:09:22,479 --> 00:09:24,479
And we find that the Bible tells us here

224
00:09:24,479 --> 00:09:26,960
that he behaved himself more wisely

225
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:29,960
than all the servants of Saul.

