00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:37,919
But I want you to notice that it says

229
00:09:37,919 --> 00:09:42,520
walk in wisdom toward them that are without.

230
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:45,679
Walk in wisdom toward them that are without.

231
00:09:45,679 --> 00:09:48,099
What is the instruction?

